  triage:title "extraction-plan.md and boundary-toml-migration.md missing Rust-native vs Python-backed statement" ;
  triage:description "Sprint A.7 acceptance criterion 4 requires an explicit statement in docs/sc-lint/extraction-plan.md and docs/sc-lint/boundary-toml-migration.md (or equivalent) identifying which checks are now Rust-native and which remain Python-backed after the manifest-policy addition. Both documents lack this statement. Fix: add a section or table to each document clearly distinguishing Rust-native checks (sc-lint-boundary Rust analyzer) from Python-backed checks (.just/ parity oracle layer)." ;
